表的代码预览员工

drop index employee_PK on employee;


alter table employee
drop foreign key FK_EMPLOYEE_雇佣_BRANCH;

drop table if exists employee;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: employee */
/*==============================================================*/
create table employee
(
employee_id varchar(20) not null comment '',
branch_name varchar(255) comment '',
phone varchar(20) comment '',
address longtext comment '',
date_be_employed date comment '',
employee_name varchar(255) comment ''
);

alter table employee comment '员工';

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: employee_PK */
/*==============================================================*/
create unique index employee_PK on employee
(
employee_id
);

alter table employee add constraint FK_EMPLOYEE_雇佣_BRANCH foreign key (branch_name)
references branch (branch_name) on delete restrict on update restrict;
